  TITLE     A novel R-stereoselective amidase from Pseudomonas sp. MCI3434 acting on piperazine-2-tert-butylcarboxamide.
  JOURNAL   Eur. J. Biochem. 271 (2004) 1580-90.
  ORGANISM  Pseudomonas sp.
